    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required Gradation 2 level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to not-assessed at Gradation 1 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for a Class II device at MRL 2. Discretization error (GCI 2.3%) and output comparison (max error 8.4%, within uncertainty bounds) confirm model fitness for purpose. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under the defined COU.",
